<div id="pf360" class="pf w18 h106" data-page-no="360"><div class="pc pc360 w18 h106"><div class="t m8a1 x10 h5f y1ec ff4 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSONS ON THE BOOK OF LUKE. </div><div class="t m5 x9 h5f y23d ff4 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"></div><div class="t m1642 x94 h4 y23d ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">26 </div><div class="t m1329 x74 h31 ya54 ff1 fs17 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON XI.—September 15, 1894. </div><div class="t m8a5 x34 h32 ya2b ff1 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SIGHT FOR THE BLIND. Luke 18 : 23-43. </div><div class="t m1ff x14 h4 y4ca ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">IN this lesson we have the remainder of the story of the young </div><div class="t m699 x3e h4 y595 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ruler, Christ&apos;s death foretold, and the healing of the blind man. </div><div class="t m156f x16 h4 yfb ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The entire chapter may easily be analyzed. Do it for yourself, </div><div class="t m23c x3e h4 ya57 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and do not be content to go on with the next lesson until you can </div><div class="t m3e8 x3e h4 y19c ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">give a: brief outline of the contents of this chapter. </div><div class="t m988 x73 h4 y8e ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m1584 x60 h4 y8a3 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Repeat the story of the rich young ruler who came to Jesus. </div><div class="t m127 x73 h4 y9e4 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m48d x60 h4 y9e4 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What question did he ask ? </div><div class="t m2b6 x73 h4 y24b ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m751 x60 h4 y9e5 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">To what did Jesus refer him ? </div><div class="t ma2 x73 h4 y34d ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m5d2 x60 h4 y34d ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What did the young man reply ? </div><div class="t m1cd x73 h4 y4cc ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m245 x60 h4 y4cc ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Who% did Jesus say that he lacked&apos;? </div><div class="t m1d0 x73 h4 y5d4 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m365 x60 h4 y5d4 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How did the ruler receive this counsel? </div><div class="t m1d2 x73 h4 yf ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7. </div><div class="t m465 x60 h4 yf ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Whaycaused his sorrow? </div><div class="t m1d5 x73 h4 y407 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">8. </div><div class="t m61d x60 h4 y407 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">When Jesus saw his sorrow, what did He say ? </div><div class="t m127 x74 h4 y408 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">9. </div><div class="t md3 x60 h4 y408 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How difficult is it for a rich man to enter into the kingdom </div><div class="t m452 x16 h4 y2c2 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of Cod? </div><div class="t me4 x14 h4 y182 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">10. </div><div class="t ma8f x60 h4 y182 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What was said by those who heard this? </div><div class="t me4 x5d h4 y13 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">11. </div><div class="t mf3e x60 h4 y15f ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What did Jesus reply to that? </div><div class="t me4 x5d h4 y5d9 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">12. </div><div class="t m1468 x5f h4 y5d9 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What did Peter say? </div><div class="t me4 x5d h4 yac8 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">13. </div><div class="t m648 x60 h4 y356 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What did Jesus say that those who leave all should receivr </div><div class="t me4 x5d h4 y238 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">14. </div><div class="t m48b x5f h4 y238 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What did Jesus then reveal to the twelve? </div><div class="t me4 x5d h4 y9b ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">15. </div><div class="t m180 x5f h4 y9b ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How minutely did He foretell His sufferings and resurrec-</div><div class="t me02 x71 h4 yd34 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tion ? </div><div class="t me4 x5d h4 y460 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">16. </div><div class="t m6da x5f h4 y460 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How much of it did the disciples understand ? </div><div class="t me4 x5d h4 y5c7 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">17. </div><div class="t m8ba x5f h4 y61b ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Why did they not understand ? See note 2. </div><div class="t me4 x5d h4 y61c ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">18. </div><div class="t m1aa x5f h4 yef ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">As they came near to Jericho, whom did they find? </div><div class="t me4 x5d h4 yf0 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">19. </div><div class="t md3 x5f h4 yc66 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How did the blind man learn of their approach? </div><div class="t mc0 x5d h4 y3e ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">20. </div><div class="t m39e x5f h4 y37 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">When he heard that Jesus of Nazareth passed by, what did </div><div class="t m107e x71 h4 y1ae ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">he cry ? </div><div class="t mc0 x48 h4 y2cd ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">21. </div><div class="t m34f x5f h4 y370 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What was said to him by those who went before? </div><div class="t mc0 x5d h4 y27b ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">22. </div><div class="t m2c6 xc h4 y27b ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What effect did this have? </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
